  <brief_title>Characteristics of Non Diabetic Hyperglycemic Inpatients</brief_title>
  <official_title>Hyperglycemic Non Diabetic (HND) Hospital Patients: Are They Different From Diabetic Hyperglycemic and Non-Hyperglycemic Non-Diabetic(NHND) Patients?</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
